      <title>火箭购买抵押公司库珀先生以94亿美元的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/rocket-to-buy-mortgage-servicer-mr-cooper-in-9-4-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在线抵押贷款提供商Rocket Cos。正在以一项价值94亿美元的全股票协议收购库珀集团公司，这将创造出一种抵押巨头，该抵押庞然大物在美国每六个抵押贷款中处理一项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/rocket-to-buy-mortgage-servicer-mr-cooper-in-9-4-billion-deal</guid>
