    <item>
      <title>拉里·芬克（Larry Fink）发誓要解锁大众的私人投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/larry-fink-vows-to-unlock-private-investments-for-the-masses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BlackRock Inc.首席执行官拉里·芬克（Larry Fink）承诺向数百万日常投资者开放私人市场，而不仅仅是富裕的少数投资者，他认为个人应该分享更多来自经济增长的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/larry-fink-vows-to-unlock-private-investments-for-the-masses</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
